      <p>{`When a tooth becomes weak, broken, or significantly damaged, its strength and function are compromised. A simple filling may not be enough to provide the necessary protection. At AnaBella Family and Cosmetic Dentistry, we offer custom-made dental crowns to restore your tooth's integrity and appearance. Our team is dedicated to guiding you through a comfortable and effective treatment process to ensure your long-term oral health.`}</p>
      <p>{`A dental crown is a durable, tooth-shaped cap that is placed over the entire visible portion of a damaged tooth, acting like a protective shield. Each crown is custom-designed to match the specific size and shape of the original tooth. Once bonded in place, it restores the tooth's strength, allowing it to function properly for chewing and biting.`}</p>
