      <p>{`Dr. Eric Kim is the newest member of our dental team. Originally from the Pacific Northwest, he studied General Biology at the University of Washington and earned his DDS from Loma Linda University. Dr. Kim is committed to helping patients and staying up-to-date with the latest advancements in dentistry.`}</p>
